---
const pageTitle = "Report Progetto Consulenza | DS-LAB";
---

<html lang="it">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code:wght@300;500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<style>
			:root {
				--primary: #284b63;
				--primary-light: #3c6e71;
				--accent: #d9d9d9;
				--bg: #ffffff;
				--text: #353535;
				--glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
			}

			* { box-sizing: border-box; }

			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
				background-color: var(--bg);
				background-image: 
					linear-gradient(rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
					linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
				background-size: 30px 30px;
				color: var(--text);
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 2rem 1rem;
			}

			.container {
				max-width: 1000px;
				width: 100%;
				background: var(--glass);
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.1);
				border-radius: 24px;
				padding: 3rem;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
			}

			h1 {
				color: var(--primary);
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				letter-spacing: -1px;
			}

			.intro {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #555;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.actions {
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}

			.btn {
				background-color: var(--primary);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: bold;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				transition: all 0.2s;
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			.btn:hover {
				background-color: var(--primary-light);
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}

			.back-link {
				display: inline-block;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				color: var(--primary);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}

			.pdf-viewer {
				width: 100%;
				height: 80vh;
				border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
				border-radius: 12px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			footer {
				margin-top: 4rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: #999;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<a href="/" class="back-link">← Torna alla Home</a>
			<h1>Report Progetto Consulenza</h1>
			
			<p class="intro">
				Questo report analizza i processi operativi e strategici del progetto di consulenza, fornendo una panoramica dettagliata delle ottimizzazioni proposte. 
				È uno strumento fondamentale per comprendere l'impatto delle soluzioni ingegneristiche sui sistemi gestionali analizzati.
			</p>

			<div class="actions">
				<a href="/progetti/report1.pdf" download class="btn">
					📄 Scarica il Report (PDF)
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="pdf-viewer">
				<iframe src="/progetti/report1.pdf" width="100%" height="100%" style="border: none;">
					Il tuo browser non supporta la visualizzazione del PDF. 
					<a href="/progetti/report1.pdf">Clicca qui per scaricarlo.</a>
				</iframe>
			</div>
		</div>

		<footer>
			&copy; 2026 Davide Santaniello — Built with Astro & Quartz
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
